    "Nevertheless, such a process is appealing to university researchers as it opens up opportunities to co-design and innovate new EPIC circuits 134, 135 at low cost and packaging effort.",
    "On the other hand, multiple efforts are underway to integrate transistors onto the same wafers as silicon photonic devices 136.",
